            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Psalm 37:21",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Yet I deny not that in case of poverty the debt was to be forgiven; but that was not by virtue of this law, but of other commands of God. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
